thread.title_full: Mystery Tackle Box reviewed by Kelsi

author: Kelsi
title: Kelsi
text: Mystery Tackle Box has a great combination of fishing lures. There's always a combination of plastics, crank baits and other forms of bass lures. It's a great way to try new products and items without breaking the bank! Defiantly would recommend. I subscribed because I recently got into bass fishing and the bass box was a perfect option to get me started.
